Title: Superseven Is Still My Name
Writer: T.J. Glenn (story), Jerry Kokich (story), Andrew Palmer (story), Scott Rhodes (screenplay), Scott Rhodes (story)
Actors: Jerry Kokich, Olivia Dunkley, Kurt Carley, Crystal Coney
Plot: An unknown assassin is killing the top agents of T.H.E.M. Superseven, Sandra West and Sparky race against time and the odds to bring the spy killing spree to an explosive end.
